KPI: Average Months Waiting 11

Months Waiting 

Drag and Drop fields in Text Mark  (Fields;  Months Waiting, cc. YoY Mths Waiting, cc. YoY Mths Waiting Down , cc. YoY Mths Waiting Up)

Edit as in gif



Formatting the Labels with Color, Font and Size

1  - Select each field and format it  (Details are given below)

2  - Select Color     

3 - Select More Color     

4 - Copy and paste the given color code   

5 - Click OK

Do the same for each field then  6 Click Apply to see if all of them match that in the snapshot.

If it does Press OK 7 



Format Details

Avg Months Waiting - Size 8

<AVG(Months Waiting)>  - Size 26, #8493a7

<AGG( cc.YoY Mths Waiting DOWN)>  - Size 9, #59a14f

<AGG(cc.YoY Mths Waiting UP)>  - Size 9, #c60000

<AGG(cc.YoY Mths Waiting)> vs PY   - Size 9, #676767


Format & De-activate Tooltip

Click Text Mark to Center,  Right click AVG(Months Waiting) to format, Right Click AGG(cc. YoY Mths Waiting) to Format, Click on Tooltip to de-activate it by unchecking the boxes.
